---
title: Sweet Soy Pork & Pepper Bowls with Cilantro Lime Lemongrass Rice
description: If you’re looking for a quick and tasty weeknight meal, look no further! This one comes together in just 20 minutes. Ground pork and bell pepper are satéed in a sweet chili sauce and served over buttery, zesty rice with a dash of cilantro. So when the kids have soccer practice, you’re working extra late, or you just want to settle into your favorite side of the couch early: these bowls are here for you.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-soy-pork-pepper-bowls-5f8ded44.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-soy-pork-pepper-bowls-60896b2580f53f214a2efdc2-d01558f2.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sweet-soy-pork-pepper-bowls-60896b2580f53f214a2efdc2
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: Asian
time required: 20 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 790 kcal
  fat: 38 g
  saturated fat: 14 g
  carbohydrates: 79 g
  sugar: 27 g
